feat: add Redis health checker for database monitoring (fl-nvu)

Implements checkRedis as a CheckFunc for the dbmon framework. Checks:
PING, INFO memory (used_memory vs maxmemory), INFO stats (evicted_keys
delta), SLOWLOG GET 10, INFO clients (connected_clients vs maxclients),
INFO replication (master_link_status, master_last_io_seconds_ago).

Uses RedisClient interface for testability without requiring a live
Redis instance. Thresholds from design spec (memory >90%, clients >80%,
replication lag >10s) with override support via RedisThresholds.

